            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/736/342.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 02:54:12 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1766877" rel="nofollow">小陈师傅</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1522963" rel="nofollow">星痕永至</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1191610" rel="nofollow">VIP涪江侠客</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D671173" rel="nofollow">戈多-Godo</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D670584" rel="nofollow">SunnyYu</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1790088" rel="nofollow">推荐</a> 的线索投递！</div>
            <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 12 月 1 日消息，经过一段时间的等待，小米今日已开启 Redmi K60 至尊版手机的澎湃 OS 正式版内测推送。</p><p><span class="accentTextColor">本次更新的版本号为 <span class="link-text-start-with-http">1.0.4.0.UMLCNXM</span>，更新大小为 6GB</span>，带来了从 MIUI 到澎湃 OS 的海量更新内容。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><span class="post-img-item"><img height="1317" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/130cfe12-387a-4436-8829-1bd275d19ef8.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE4MS5wbmc=,t_100,g_3,y_18,x_18,a_0/format,f_auto" title="小米 Redmi K60 至尊版手机推送澎湃 OS 正式版内测更新" width="1179" /></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span class="post-img-item"><img height="1264" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/29f38c59-9344-4cdc-b766-576129f4982b.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE4My5wbmc=,t_100,g_3,y_18,x_18,a_0/format,f_auto" title="小米 Redmi K60 至尊版手机推送澎湃 OS 正式版内测更新" width="1192" /></span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/732/472.htm" target="_blank"><span class="post-img-item">据IT之家此前报道</span></a><span class="post-img-item">，Redmi K60 / Pro 两款机型已率先升级澎湃 OS 开发版，而&nbsp;Redmi K60 至尊版直接到了正式版内测。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="968" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/38dd7d56-7770-4bab-bce2-08dd77b0fbe7.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="小米 Redmi K60 至尊版手机推送澎湃 OS 正式版内测更新" width="677" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="589" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/10/6138b0ca-7e29-4964-a2d6-def32512a934.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="小米 Redmi K60 至尊版手机推送澎湃 OS 正式版内测更新" width="1015" /></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span class="post-img-item"></span>根据小米此前的承诺，Redmi K60 至尊版手机将支持 5 年 OTA 更新，4 次<a class="s_tag" href="https://android.ithome.com/" target="_blank">安卓</a>大版本升级。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="图片 1" height="920" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/8/1211076a-c9b5-409b-8e3e-118f785c0bb4.jpeg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="小米 Redmi K60 至尊版手机推送澎湃 OS 正式版内测更新" width="690" /></p><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
